metadata.name: Chill Out
metadata.description:
Chill Out appeared as an exercise where I tried to mix the characters that appeared in my imagination together with my technique of perspective. It also incorporates my universe of symbols. The essence is the party chill out after lots of dancing, deep beautiful relaxation. This my ideal chillout scene, many friends in a very entertaining house. 

First buyer gets original 1/1  handmade artwork.*
*Shipping not included
